ðŸ”¹ 2. Install Grafana

  Windows:
  Just run the .msi installer â†’ it will set up Grafana as a service.
  
  Linux (Debian/Ubuntu):
  
  sudo dpkg -i grafana-enterprise_<version>_amd64.deb
  sudo systemctl start grafana-server
  sudo systemctl enable grafana-server
  
  
  Linux (RHEL/CentOS):
  
